Sure! Here's a list of 5 fruits that are native to different countries and do not contain the letter "E" in their names, along with their countries of origin:

\begin{enumerate}
  \item Mangostan - Indonesia
  \item Tamarind - India
  \item Rambutan - Malaysia
  \item Papaya - Mexico
  \item Açaí - Brazil
\end{enumerate}

These fruits are often grown organically in their native regions.
